704439f-c.text:
Franklin Avenue, at uincy Street. View 1,I show an old frame
. at the southwest corner of the intersection. View 3 shows the
buildings adjoining the southeast crber. 'ote the old frame
dwelling hemmed in between tow apartment buildings.
